<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Loan Application System</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; }
        .header { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .stats { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .stat-card { background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; flex: 1; }
        .api-links { margin: 20px 0; }
        .api-links a { display: block; margin: 5px 0; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; }
        .api-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Loan Application System</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the AWS Database Modernization Workshop</p>
        <p><strong>@ViewBag.DatabaseStatus</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>Applications</h3>
            <p><strong>@ViewBag.ApplicationCount</strong> total applications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <h3>Customers</h3>
            <p><strong>@ViewBag.CustomerCount</strong> registered customers</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Available API Endpoints:</h2>
    <div class="api-links">
        <a href="/api/applications">GET /api/applications - List all applications</a>
        <a href="/api/applications/count">GET /api/applications/count - Application count</a>
        <a href="/api/applications/status/Approved">GET /api/applications/status/Approved - Approved applications</a>
        <a href="/api/customers">GET /api/customers - List all customers</a>
        <a href="/api/customers/count">GET /api/customers/count - Customer count</a>
        <a href="/api/customers/1">GET /api/customers/1 - Get customer by ID</a>
    </div>

    <h2>üìö Workshop Documentation:</h2>
    <div class="api-links">
        <a href="/docs">üèóÔ∏è Architecture & Database Documentation</a>
        <a href="/docs/migration">üöÄ Migration Strategy & Phases</a>
    </div>

    <h2>Workshop Migration Phases:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Phase 1:</strong> Lift & Shift to AWS RDS SQL Server</li>
        <li><strong>Phase 2:</strong> Modernize to Aurora PostgreSQL</li>
        <li><strong>Phase 3:</strong> Optimize with DynamoDB Integration</li>
    </ul>
    <p><em>üìñ For detailed information, visit the <a href="/docs">complete documentation</a>.</em></p>
</body>
</html>